          <p class="callout-text">The tension is real. Teachers want comprehension insight. Students need safety to respond honestly. V1 doesn't resolve it, and that's intentional. <em>The V2 hypothesis is AI-summarized misconception reports</em> rather than raw responses. Teachers get instructional signal without individual exposure. That's worth designing carefully, not shipping fast.</p>
